      "body" : "For the first commit, is there no check that if you send a getblocktxn for an old block, you get disconnected? If not, I feel that the would be better (treating old blocks and unknown blocks identically).",
      "created_at" : "2016-07-28T18:33:39Z",
      "html_url" : "https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/pull/8408#issuecomment-235984691",
      "id" : 235984691,
